    "body": "I suppose the flow would be, please confirm @dapplion :\r\n- New Rest api to produce local blinded block\r\n- Cache full ExecutionPayload by root\r\n- New Rest api to publish local blinded block, combine with the cached payload above to create the regular SignedBeaconBlock\r\n\r\nTwo questions I have:\r\n- Need 2 new apis, or new header for existing produce/publish block api at https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs , otherwise our validator cannot work with beacon nodes from other clients\r\n- Fallback urls at `vc` may not work if the local blinded block is published to a different beacon node",
